1. DEFINITIONS (정의)
================================================================================

"Software" means the BabyHippo source code, documentation, and all associated 
files distributed under this license.

"Creator" means the original author(s) who created the Software.
  - Creator Wallet: 0x99779F19376c4740d4F555083F6dcB2B47C76bF5

"Contributor" means any person who modifies, extends, or improves the Software.

"Contribution Score" means a numeric value (0.0 to 1.0) calculated by the 
PHAM Sign system based on the significance of code changes.

"Revenue" means any monetary income, tokens, or value generated through the 
use of this Software in commercial products or services.

"Ledger" means the blockchain-based record of all contributions and their 
corresponding scores.

